{"word":"H314 - אַחֲרֹון - ʼachărôwn - akh-ar-one' - After","slug":"H314","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אַחֲרֹון</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʼachărôwn"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>akh-ar-one'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>After"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D0;&#x05D7;&#x05E8;&#x05DF;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D0;&#x05D7;&#x05E8;&#x05D9;&#x05DF; - 'acha&#x0306;ryo&#x0302;n  'acha&#x0306;ro&#x0302;n</b> - <i>akh-ar-one', akh-ar-one'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H309\">H309</a>; <i>hinder</i>; generally <i>late</i> or <i>last</i>; specifically (as facing the east) <i>western: - </i>after (-ward), to come, following, hind (-er, -ermost, -most), last, latter, rereward, ut(ter)most."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H268\">H268</a>, <a href=\"#/H309\">H309</a>, <a href=\"#/H310\">H310</a>, <a href=\"#/H312\">H312</a>, <a href=\"#/H313\">H313</a>, <a href=\"#/H315\">H315</a>, <a href=\"#/H316\">H316</a>, <a href=\"#/H3186\">H3186</a>, <a href=\"#/H319\">H319</a>, <a href=\"#/H322\">H322</a>, <a href=\"#/H323\">H323</a>, <a href=\"#/H325\">H325</a>, <a href=\"#/H326\">H326</a>, <a href=\"#/H327\">H327</a>"}]}